#String tooltip
This bot lets you to replant turnip field. Choose an area with 'crop(Turnip)' specialization for planting. In order to stockpile the turnips - create new area and have a turnip in the 'Put' section. Choose an area with seed barrels for seed collecting with 'seed(Turnip)' specialization. Optionally, choose and area with 'trough' specialization for troughs in order to collect left over swill.